sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant Server
    participant Auth

    User->>Browser: open /accounts/login
    Browser->>Server: GET /accounts/login
    Server-->>Browser: render login form

    User->>Browser: submit credentials
    Browser->>Server: POST /accounts/login
    Server->>Auth: authenticate(credentials)
    alt valid
        Auth-->>Server: return user
        Server-->>Browser: redirect to dashboard
    else invalid
        Auth-->>Server: None
        Server-->>Browser: render form with error
    end
